1. Has your mother a new car? — Yes, she has a new car.
2. Is this a red pen? — Yes, this is a red pen.
3. Have you got a cat? - No, I haven't got a cat.
4. Have you many friends? - Yes, I have many friends.
5. Is this pen red? — No, this pen is not red.
6. Are those houses white? — No, those houses are not white.
